sources.title: Shock (restored, colorized) (1946, film noir, imdb score: 6.3)
sources.description: Shock is a 1946 American film noir directed by Alfred L. Werker and starring Vincent Price , Lynn Bari and Frank Latimore . It was produced and distributed by 20th Century Fox .
